  <span class="target" id="ecommerce-platform-zen-cart"></span><div class="section" id="zen-cart-store-integration">
<h1>Zen Cart Store Integration<a class="headerlink" href="#zen-cart-store-integration" title="Permalink to this headline">Â¶</a></h1>
<ol class="arabic">
<li><p class="first">Download the <a class="reference external" href="https://www.talkable.com/zencart/curebit_checkout_0.0.2.zip">Zen Cart Curebit Add-On</a> and unzip it to your Zen Cart catalog
directory (eg /var/www/zencart).</p>
</li>
<li><p class="first">Login to your administrator console (eg <a class="reference external" href="http://yourstoredomain.com/admin_console">http://yourstoredomain.com/admin_console</a>)
with your administrator credentials.</p>
</li>
<li><p class="first">Click <strong>Modules</strong> &rarr; <strong>Order Total</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li><p class="first">Click <strong>Curebit Checkout</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li><p class="first">Click <strong>install</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li><div class="first line-block">
<div class="line">Enter your Curebit Site ID and enable by selecting <em>true</em>.</div>
<div class="line">You can get your Curebit Site ID from your Curebit dashboard after you log in and create a site.</div>
</div>
</li>
<li><p class="first">Click <strong>Update</strong>.</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p><br></p>
<p><a class="reference internal" href="../verify.html#ecommerce-verify"><em>Verifying Integration Instructions</em></a></p>
